# NOTE (deployment): unlike the local dev repo, data/, index/, static/ and
# "AIFI latest/" ARE committed here — the app reads the manifest/chunks/vector
# index/served PDFs at runtime, and the 34 baked explanation guides are
# hand-authored (not regenerable by a script). They are public RBI documents
# and small (~60 MB total), so they ship with the deploy.
